{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"45685feb4a","title":"毛泽东在北京卫戍区关于部队战备野营拉练总结报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ce6b6191f","index":0,"year":1970,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"45685feb4a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5eb8259ee2","type":"title","text":"在北京卫戍区关于部队战备野营拉练总结报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"45685feb4a"},{"id":"fcb701ff0e","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"45685feb4a"},{"id":"d29cca3f52","type":"appellation","text":"林彪同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"45685feb4a"},{"id":"6755f44f89","type":"paragraph","text":"此件可阅，我看很好。请你和黄永胜同志商量一下，全军是否利用冬季实行长途野营训练一次，每个军可分两批（或不分批），每批两个月，实行官兵团结、军民团结。三支、两军者不在内。但大、中、小学（高年级）学生是否利用寒假也可以实行野营训练一个月。工厂是否可以抽少数工人（例如四分之一，但生产不能减少）进行野营练习。请与中央各同志一商。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"45685feb4a"},{"id":"19d3be480d","type":"paragraph","text":"如不这样训练，就会变成老爷兵。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"45685feb4a"}],"page":{"id":"fe7210d889","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"45685feb4a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}